@page "/"

<PageTitle>ModernMediator — Blazor Server</PageTitle>

<h1>ModernMediator Blazor Server Sample</h1>

<p>
    This sample demonstrates <strong>ModernMediator</strong> used directly inside Razor components
    via dependency injection. Queries are dispatched from <code>@@code</code> blocks, results are
    bound to component state, and the <code>LoggingBehavior</code> pipeline output is visible in the
    server console window.
</p>

<div class="alert alert-primary">
    <strong>What to try:</strong> Navigate to the
    <a href="/animals">Animals</a> page to see mediator dispatch in action.
    Watch the server console for logging output from <code>LoggingBehavior</code>.
</div>
